{
  "texts": [
    "Also, students found CodeTailor as more engaging and could apply significantly more supported elements from the scaffolded practice to the posttest after using CodeTailor than just getting the correct solution.",
    "Overall, most students preferred CodeTailor for learning versus just receiving an AI-generated code solution.",
    "The funding came from the National Science Foundation award 2143028.",
    "Any conclusions expressed in this material do not necessarily reflect the views of NSF.Figure 1:1Figure 1: The CodeTailor interface contains a programming area on the left and a pop-up personalized Parsons puzzle as support on the right.",
    "It provides timely feedback after checking (G) and allows students to copy (H) the finished solution (I)."
  ]
}